dc:description: Fibula in fair condition. Leech type with long open sheath for pin, now missing. Bow has incised line decoration: several deep grooves in a geometric pattern, with light, narrow, horizontal bands over much of the surface. Hollow bow is partially broken away on the underside. Light green corroded surface with encrusted dirt.
